General Village Accessories
Revised 5/23/2025

Department 56 has created a host of General Village Accessories that are designed to be incorporated into a specific collection and/or subseries as a collector would deem. Over the years, this term has been changed to Cross Product in an effort to accentuate the way that some of the items may be used across village lines.

In this section, items are listed under category types so that a collector may reference all of the like items and determine which ones best fit their requirements for display. Department 56 has altered its numbering system through the years which has caused products not to be listed in numerical sequence. Only those items that are not part of a General Village Accessory subseries are referenced here.
